<title>CSS Overflow Test: Root element's scrollbar-gutter is accounted for in fixed-pos positioning</title>
<title><style>
:root {
  scrollbar-gutter: stable both-edges;
}
body {
  margin: 0;
}
.fixed {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  background: green;
  position: fixed;
}
</style></title>

